## Summary

**What changed:** Added a single-line `.replace("--bin yoyo", "--bin yyds")` in `run_fixture_command` (`src/eval_fixtures.rs`, line 644) that rewrites stale binary references at command execution time.

**Why:** The binary was renamed from `yoyo` to `yyds`, but 275 fixture JSON files still reference `cargo run --bin yoyo`. Rather than editing 275 files individually, this transparent rewrite in the fixture runner fixes all of them at once.

**Verification:**
• `cargo fmt -- --check` ✅
• `cargo build` ✅
• `cargo test --bin yyds` ✅
• `cargo run --bin yyds -- eval fixtures score --sample 20` → **20/20 passed, zero "no bin target" errors** ✅

